17. Rd3 { 17.R3e2?  Ba6∓  . } 17... Ba6 18. Rc3 Rxc3 19. Qxc3 Nf6
{ The knight already accomplished his mission so we bring it back to the natural square. }
20. Ne5 Bb7 21. f3 h6 22. Rc1 Qd6 { The d4-pawn requires constant protection. }
23. Nxf7 Rxf7 24. e5 Qd7 25. exf6 Rxf6 { We're totally fine. } *

