19. e5 Nf8
{ A familiar rerouting of the knight, also clearing d8 for the rooks. } 20. Kh2
Ng6 21. f4 Ne7 22. g3 Qh5 23. Ne3 Red8
{ Our knight has landed on an excellent square and our queen is in no real danger as there is no way to attack it. Black's position is good. }
