18. Bb1 Red8 19. d5 exd5 20. exd5 Qf8
{ Black intends ...Nf6 next with huge pressure on the central pawn.   Just to show why  20...Qf8  is so good:  20...Qd6  21.Nd4!  and now  21...Qxd5  loses to  22.Be4+-  . }
