14... Bxg2 15. Kxg2 Nc6
{ A little tactical resource that allows Black to equalize on the spot. } 16.
Nxc6 Qd5+ 17. e4 Qxc6 18. d5 exd5 19. exd5 Qd6
{ This type of major piece ending is quite drawish, the central pawn is not dangerous. }
