{ The queen trade would be quite good for Black as then the king would seat nicely on e7. }
10. Qxc4 Bg7 11. Be2 Qa5 12. O-O Qb4
{ Insisting on the queen trade, this time is hard to avoid and the resulting position will be slightly better for Black, to a large extent thanks to the strong bishop on g7. }
