9. Ne2 cxd4 10. cxd4 Bb4+ 11. Bd2 Qa5
{ Not the only way to react but the simplest, I think. We aim for the endgame where our king will immediately go to the nice square on e7. }
12. a3 Bxd2+ 13. Qxd2 Rc8
{ Again, we do not help White by taking on d2 but rather accept the trade on our conditions! }
14. Qxa5 Nxa5 15. f4 Ke7 16. Kf2 Ba4 { Black is doing very well. } *

