15. Bb5 f5 16. exf5 e4 17. Nc4 Rxf5
{ Black is doing well, one logical plan is to trade bishops on b5 and install a knight on d3. After that, d5 will be harder to defend and also White's kingside starts to feel a little vulnerable. }
