13. Ke2 { Clearly intending Be3 and solving the king issue. } 13... Nd4+
{ It's important not to give White time to consolidate with Be3. } 14. Nxd4
Bxd4 15. Rb1 Bg4+ 16. Ke1 Rac8 17. Be2 Bd7
{ Again very accurate, and the point is similar to the one in the previous comment.  After the bishop trade, it would be much easier for White to develop @@StartBracket@@the rook would get to d1 quickly etc.@@EndBracket@@ whereas now it is still problematic for White to finish his development.  Black has nice chances here, I believe. }
