10... Kh8 11. e5 cxd4 { Play now gets a very forcing character } 12. Bd3
{ The best way to set up the battery threat with Qe4.   12.Qe4?  Qd5∓  And White is not in time for Bd3.   12.cxd4?  Nc6  13.Nf3  Bb4+!  transposes to the variation  @@StartFEN@@rnbq1r1k/pp2bpp1/4p2p/2p4P/3PP1Q1/2P5/P4PP1/1RB1KBNR w K - 2 11@@EndFEN@@  11.Nf3  cxd4  12.cxd4  Nc6  13.e5  Bb4+  . }
