Nxf6 15. Qg6 Qe8
{ Otherwise Bxh6 is coming.  White has to trade queens because he still has to regain his pawn on d4, and after that, Black gets a good position. }
16. cxd4 Qxg6 17. hxg6 b6 18. Nf3 Bb7 { And Black is doing well. } *

