{ is the other logical move but after the natural sequence } 12... cxd4 13.
cxd4 Na5 14. Bd3 Rc8 { Black is doing well. } 15. Qg4 Nc4
{ Unlike the same position with the knight on f4, here Black has nothing to fear as White can't really attack our kingside effectively }
16. Bxc4 { 16.Bh6?  Qxd4-+  .   16.Nh5  g6  . } 16... Rxc4 17. Rbc1 Rxc1 18.
Rxc1 g6 19. Bh6 Re8 { The position remains balanced. } *

