15... Rc8 { and there is no Rxg7 anymore. } 16. Bb2 { 16.Rxg7?  Rxc1+-+  . }
16... Nf6 17. Qe3 Qc7 18. Rc1 Qd6
{ The position is dynamically balanced, a possible line could be } 19. a3
{ 19.e5?  Qb4+-+  . } 19... Rxc1+ 20. Bxc1 Qc6 21. Rxg7 { Is also a draw. }
21... Qc3+ 22. Bd2 Qa1+ 23. Ke2 Kxg7 24. Qxh6+ Kg8
{ White has to repeat moves once again as otherwise, Black wins. } 25. Qg5+ Kh8
