8. Nxd5 exd5
{ This leads to a symmetrical structure where White doesn't have much. } 9. Nf3
Bb4+ 10. Bd2 Qe7+ { This check is annoying for White. } 11. Qe2
{ 11.Be2  Bb5  is also equal. } 11... Nc6 { And the position is equal. } *

