12... Nxe7 13. d5
{ With this move, White gets rid of the isolated pawn but of course, here it doesn't give him any advantage. }
13... exd5 14. Nxd5 Nxd5 15. Qxd5 Qxd5 16. Bxd5 Nf4 17. Be4 Be6
{ With full equality. } *

